text:
BREAKING: DOH announces 630 new COVID-19 cases in the country — 467 detected in the last three days, while 163 were part of the validation backlog.

Total case count rises to 30,682, with 8,143 recoveries and 1,177 deaths.

Live blog: https://t.co/QW3zhOBVz4 https://t.co/47F6rnEUER
